The `{% require_js %}` tag accepts a `position` param, which lets you place it in either the head or the footer!

```{% require_js position="head" %}
  {# I go in &lt;head&gt;! #}
{% end_require_js %}```
Check out the parameters table in the documentation for more info:
<https://developers.HubSpot.com/docs/cms/hubl/tags#require-js>
